verse.lines:
Have mercy on me, O my God
According to Your grace;
According to Your tender Love
Blot out transgressions great;
For I acknowledge all my sin,
Before my face they stand;
Against You only have I sinned,
There's evil on my hands.

O purge me now and I'll be clean,
As clean and white as snow;
O wash me in the Blood of Christ,
Make me Your gladness know;
Create in me a clean heart,
Lord, Renew me thoroughly;
Restore salvation's joy again, Uphold me tenderly.
